                            <comment id="16721476" author="janhoy" created="Fri, 14 Dec 2018 14:46:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;To reproduce:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Edit &lt;tt&gt;solr/example/techproducts/solr/techproducts/conf/solrconfig.xml&lt;/tt&gt; and add this section
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-xml&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;requestHandler name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;/admin/ping&quot;&lt;/span&gt; class=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;solr.PingRequestHandler&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;!-- relative paths are resolved against the data dir --&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;str name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;healthcheckFile&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;server-enabled.txt&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/str&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;lst name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;invariants&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;str name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;qt&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;/query&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/str&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;!-- handler to delegate to --&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;str name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;q&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;*:*&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/str&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/lst&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/requestHandler&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;


&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Start with &lt;tt&gt;bin/solr -e techproducts&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Load the core overview for &quot;techproducts&quot; &lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:8983/solr/#/techproducts/core-overview&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://localhost:8983/solr/#/techproducts/core-overview&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;In the right-hand part of the screen there is now an &quot;enable ping&quot; button, which does not work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;image-wrap&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/12951823/12951823_pingbutton.png&quot; width=&quot;400&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px solid black&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=a3836903&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;a3836903&quot;&gt;a3836903&lt;/a&gt;,&#160;I have not tested your patch. Would you care to update it to current master and add a CHANGES.txt entry?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
